  :synonyms ("λ-calculus" "lambda calculus" "LAMBDA CALCULUS")
  :discipline (:math :logic :cs-theory)
  :kind (:formal-system :model-of-computation)
  :heritage-narrative "A formal system in mathematical logic for expressing computation using variable binding and substitution; introduced by Alonzo Church in the 1930s; foundational to functional programming languages."
