  :synonyms ("garbage collection" "GC" "automatic memory management")
  :discipline (:computing)
  :kind (:algorithm :abstraction)
  :heritage-narrative "Automatic reclamation of memory that a program is no longer using; invented for Lisp in 1959, now standard in most managed runtimes."
